{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CanvasGradient","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient/addColorStop\"><code>addColorStop()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Canvas API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>CanvasGradient</code></strong> interface represents an <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opaque_data_type\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">opaque object</a> describing a gradient. It is returned by the methods <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createLinearGradient\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient()</code></a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createConicGradient\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createConicGradient()</code></a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createRadialGradient\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createRadialGradient()</code></a>.</p>\n<p>It can be used as a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillStyle\" title=\"fillStyle\"><code>fillStyle</code></a> or <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeStyle\" title=\"strokeStyle\"><code>strokeStyle</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>As an opaque object, there is no exposed property.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"canvasgradient.addcolorstop\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient/addColorStop\"><code>CanvasGradient.addColorStop()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Adds a new stop, defined by an <code>offset</code> and a <code>color</code>, to the gradient.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/canvas.html#canvasgradient","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.CanvasGradient"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CanvasGradient","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Creator methods in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a>.</li>\n  <li>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> element and its associated interface, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The CanvasGradient interface represents an opaque object describing a gradient. It is returned by the methods CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient(), CanvasRenderingContext2D.createConicGradient() or CanvasRenderingContext2D.createRadialGradient().","popularity":0.0017,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:07:36.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CanvasGradient","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CanvasGradient","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CanvasGradient","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CanvasGradient","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/canvasgradient","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/canvasgradient/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/bf30e32f3b51f59080f2c76795beadb247a551eb","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient","title":"CanvasGradient"}],"pageTitle":"CanvasGradient - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}